Forces each player to play the tank at least once before Map change.

-convars-
"tank_control_disable", "0", "if set, no Forces each player to play the tank at once,1=disabled"

-commands-
  *for adm
  "sm_settank" "sm_settank <player> - force this player will become the tank"
  "sm_clearteam" "clear who_has_been_tank_arraylist for both team, useful when map change."
